Text:
Cracking Instructions:

1.	Open Cookie.app and proceed to your customized setup
2.	Go to menu Cookie > Purchase Cookie
3.	Enter any registration info you want and a bogus serial number, such as “1234567890”
4.	The app will tell you the registration number is invalid, ignore that message and restart the app
5.	Go back to menu Cookie > Purchase Cookie and you can see your registration info which has been saved
6.	Enjoy the app!
